uld be consulted.', 'Metabolism, Antagonism', NULL, NULL, 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/184456/', '[1] "Product Information. Aralen (chloroquine)." Sanofi Winthrop Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.[2] "Product Information. Hydroxychloroquine Sulfate (hydroxychloroquine)." Prasco Laboratories, Cincinnati, OH.[3] "Product Information. Plaquenil (R). (hydroxychloroquine)." Sanofi Winthrop Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767363026);
